The paper uses techniques from network analysis, information retrieval, and data mining to study the geopolitical relationships between countries using Wikipedia data. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Social and Information Retrieval (cs.SI), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Digital Libraries (cs.DL), Social and Information Networks (cs.SOC), and Cybersecurity and Privacy (cs.CYBER).
